gapminder %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = log(gdpPercap), y = lifeExp)) +

将三个模型放在一张图中，直观地比较

library(colorspace)

model_colors <- colorspace::qualitative_hcl(4, palette = "dark 2")
# model_colors <- c("darkorange", "purple", "cyan4")

gapminder %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = log(gdpPercap), y = lifeExp)) +
  geom_point(alpha = 0.2) +
  geom_smooth(
    method = "lm",
    aes(color = "OLS", fill = "OLS") # model 1
  ) +
  geom_smooth(
    method = "lm", formula = y ~ splines::bs(x, df = 3),
    aes(color = "Cubic Spline", fill = "Cubic Spline") # model 2
  ) +
  geom_smooth(
    method = "loess",
    aes(color = "LOESS", fill = "LOESS") # model 3
  ) +
  scale_color_manual(name = "Models", values = model_colors) +
  scale_fill_manual(name = "Models", values = model_colors) +
  theme(legend.position = "top")

broom

broom 包可以规整常见模型的输出结果为 tibble

tidy()

broom::tidy() 提取模型输出结果的主要信息为一个 tibble，参数保持默认时，各列包括 coefficients 的点估计量、估计量的标准误、t-statistics 和 p 值

library(broom)

tidy(out)
# # A tibble: 7 x 5
#   term              estimate     std.error statistic   p.value
#   <chr>                <dbl>         <dbl>     <dbl>     <dbl>
# 1 (Intercept)        4.78e+1 0.340            141.   0        
# 2 gdpPercap          4.50e-4 0.0000235         19.2  3.24e- 74
# 3 pop                6.57e-9 0.00000000198      3.33 9.01e-  4
# 4 continentAmericas  1.35e+1 0.600             22.5  5.19e- 98
# 5 continentAsia      8.19e+0 0.571             14.3  4.06e- 44
# 6 continentEurope    1.75e+1 0.625             28.0  6.34e-142
# 7 continentOceania   1.81e+1 1.78              10.1  1.59e- 23
# 参数conf.int设置为TRUE，可以将系数的置信区间作为最后两列
tidy(out, conf.int = TRUE)
# # A tibble: 7 x 7
#   term              estimate    std.error statistic   p.value conf.low conf.high
#   <chr>                <dbl>        <dbl>     <dbl>     <dbl>    <dbl>     <dbl>
# 1 (Intercept)        4.78e+1      3.40e-1    141.   0          4.71e+1   4.85e+1
# 2 gdpPercap          4.50e-4      2.35e-5     19.2  3.24e- 74  4.03e-4   4.96e-4
# 3 pop                6.57e-9      1.98e-9      3.33 9.01e-  4  2.70e-9   1.04e-8
# 4 continentAmericas  1.35e+1      6.00e-1     22.5  5.19e- 98  1.23e+1   1.47e+1
# 5 continentAsia      8.19e+0      5.71e-1     14.3  4.06e- 44  7.07e+0   9.31e+0
# 6 continentEurope    1.75e+1      6.25e-1     28.0  6.34e-142  1.62e+1   1.87e+1
# 7 continentOceania   1.81e+1      1.78e+0     10.1  1.59e- 23  1.46e+1   2.16e+1
out %>%
  tidy(conf.int = TRUE) %>%
  filter(!term %in% c("(Intercept)")) %>%
  ggplot(aes(
    x = reorder(term, estimate), y = estimate,
    ymin = conf.low, ymax = conf.high
  )) +
  geom_pointrange() +
  coord_flip() +
  labs(x = "", y = "OLS Estimate")

argument()

broom::augment() 返回一个数据框，这个数据框是在原始数据框的基础上，增加了模型的 fitted values（.fitted）、残差（.resid）、拟合值的标准误（.se.fit）等列。

augment(out)
# # A tibble: 1,704 x 10
#    lifeExp gdpPercap      pop continent .fitted .resid    .hat .sigma .cooksd

# # ... with 1,694 more rows, and 1 more variable: .std.resid <dbl>
out %>% augment() %>%
  ggplot(mapping = aes(x = lifeExp, y = .fitted)) +
  geom_point()

glance()

broom::glance() 也会返回 tibble，但只有一行，内容实际上是summary()输出结果的最底下一行，包括 F-statistic、model deviance、r-squared 等信息。

glance(out)
# # A tibble: 1 x 12
#   r.squared adj.r.squared sigma statistic   p.value    df logLik    AIC    BIC
#       <dbl>         <dbl> <dbl>     <dbl>     <dbl> <dbl>  <dbl>  <dbl>  <dbl>
# 1     0.582         0.581  8.37      394. 3.94e-317     6 -6034. 12084. 12127.
# # ... with 3 more variables: deviance <dbl>, df.residual <int>, nobs <int>

应用

penguins <-
  palmerpenguins::penguins %>%
  drop_na()

penguins %>%
  group_nest(species) %>%
  mutate(model = purrr::map(data, ~ lm(bill_depth_mm ~ bill_length_mm, data = .))) %>%
  mutate(glance = purrr::map(model, ~ broom::glance(.))) %>%
  tidyr::unnest(glance)
# # A tibble: 3 x 15
#   species      data model r.squared adj.r.squared sigma statistic  p.value    df
#   <fct>   <list<ti> <lis>     <dbl>         <dbl> <dbl>     <dbl>    <dbl> <dbl>
# 1 Adelie  [146 x 7] <lm>      0.149         0.143 1.13       25.2 1.51e- 6     1
# 2 Chinst~  [68 x 7] <lm>      0.427         0.418 0.866      49.2 1.53e- 9     1
# 3 Gentoo  [119 x 7] <lm>      0.428         0.423 0.749      87.5 7.34e-16     1
# # ... with 6 more variables: logLik <dbl>, AIC <dbl>, BIC <dbl>,
# #   deviance <dbl>, df.residual <int>, nobs <int>
fit_ols <- function(df) {
  lm(body_mass_g ~ bill_depth_mm + bill_length_mm, data = df)
}


out_tidy <- penguins %>%
  group_nest(species) %>%
  mutate(model = purrr::map(data, fit_ols)) %>%
  mutate(tidy = purrr::map(model, ~ broom::tidy(.))) %>%
  tidyr::unnest(tidy) %>%
  dplyr::filter(!term %in% "(Intercept)")

out_tidy
# # A tibble: 6 x 8
#   species                 data model  term  estimate std.error statistic p.value
#   <fct>     <list<tibble[,7]>> <list> <chr>    <dbl>     <dbl>     <dbl>   <dbl>
# 1 Adelie             [146 x 7] <lm>   bill~    164.       25.1      6.51 1.17e-9
# 2 Adelie             [146 x 7] <lm>   bill~     64.8      11.5      5.64 8.88e-8
# 3 Chinstrap           [68 x 7] <lm>   bill~    159.       43.3      3.67 4.98e-4
# 4 Chinstrap           [68 x 7] <lm>   bill~     23.8      14.7      1.62 1.11e-1
# 5 Gentoo             [119 x 7] <lm>   bill~    255.       40.0      6.37 4.01e-9
# 6 Gentoo             [119 x 7] <lm>   bill~     54.7      12.7      4.30 3.54e-5
out_tidy %>%
  ggplot(aes(
    x = species, y = estimate,
    ymin = estimate - 2 * std.error,
    ymax = estimate + 2 * std.error,
    color = term
  )) +
  geom_pointrange(position = position_dodge(width = 0.25)) +
  theme(legend.position = "top") +
